{"tid":1205761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一百萬人出咗嚟包圍晒你，警察有冇諗過 放低武器投降","createTime":"2019-06-11T23:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T00:14:47.000Z","uid":43785,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c8cacd517473003914f43e4e8cb1219dd535aa07","tid":1205761,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:24:20.000Z","msg":"係外國，一百萬人包圍 乜嘢政權都好， 其實已經可以叫佢哋放低武器投降。<br />\n你試下一百萬人圍住白宮， 一粒子彈都唔使開， 特朗普都倒台啦。<br />\n<br />\n我唔明點解香港人咁 低能， 比台灣佬笑， 畀法國佬笑，69當日， 我哋啲人多過警察哋咁多， 你警察唔投降，唔通要我哋普通市民投降咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「你放低武器投降，咪畀你哋走囉。」<br />\n香港人總係過唔到呢個心理關口唔敢講呢句， 其實台灣太陽花學運都係，總係唔敢叫警察解除裝備，民為貴君為輕， 當咁多市民一齊反對嘅時候， 世上所有民主政權都應該會到台。<br />\n<br />\n用最和平既方式解除警察武裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e9834ae467fc4c127b83122a2dcf6c470fc208","tid":1205761,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051f1a737b570a3da9aabdeb7b76108bf9e1026c","tid":1205761,"uid":254801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:57:11.000Z","msg":"我啱啱淨係經過大埔火車站，已經見十幾隻犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25bb59fbce1b6780b69a155d9371f397eb8ee20","tid":1205761,"uid":61653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:59:48.000Z","msg":"最大問題當權者知香港人唔會用暴力<br />\n唔用暴力佢地點會驚"},{"pid":"204faa96e191ff83c8b9dd27d9491cf0379a3148","tid":1205761,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a25bb59fbce1b6780b69a155d9371f397eb8ee20","tid":1205761,"uid":61653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:59:48.000Z","msg":"最大問題當權者知香港人唔會用暴力<br />\n唔用暴力